                        <h3 class="lesson-title">1. Binary Basics</h3>
                        <p class="lesson-summary">Start your journey into binary by learning how to convert everyday numbers into computer code! Discover the simple patterns that let you switch between binary (the computer's 1s and 0s) and denary (our normal numbers).</p>
