                    <div class="lesson-card">
                       <h3 class="lesson-title">2. Hex Power! The Binary Shortcut</h3>
                       <p class="lesson-summary">Binary code can get super long! Discover Hexadecimal ('Hex') – a cool shortcut using numbers 0-9 *and* letters A-F to represent chunks of binary much faster.</p>
                       <a href="Y7_T6_L2.html" class="zelda-button">Start Lesson</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="lesson-card">
                       <h3 class="lesson-title">3. Binary Conversion Master</h3>
                       <p class="lesson-summary">Master the art of converting numbers between binary and denary! Learn the tricks to quickly switch between the number systems computers use and the ones we use every day.</p>
                       <a href="Y7_T6_L3.html" class="zelda-button">Start Lesson</a>
                    </div>
